gh.asteroids1

Class BaseVectorShape

  • java.lang.Object
    • gh.asteroids1.BaseVectorShape
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Asteroid, Bullet, Ship

    public class BaseVectorShape
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the commonality that is the Asteroids game objects. Designed to act as the superclass from which all other game objects (vector shapes) are derived.
